{"id": 2869, "title": "Ticket #2869: Add attribute to denote TotalSlotCpus for pSlot queries", "description": "<blockquote>\nWe have <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalCpus\" title=\"Total Cpus\">TotalCpus</a></span> &amp;&amp; Cpus but you can have multiple pSlots on a single machine so it would be nice to denote the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotCpus\" title=\"Total Slot Cpus\">TotalSlotCpus</a></span> so folks can perform simple queries like:\n\n<p></p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">condor_status -format \"%s\\t\" Name -format \"%d\\t\" TotalSlotCpus -format \"%d\\t\" Cpus -format \"%d%%\\n\" \"((TotalSlotCpus - Cpus) /\n(TotalSlotCpus * 1.0)) * 100\" -constraint \"PartitionableSlot =?= TRUE\"\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>To obtain pSlot utilization across their pool.  This would help to determine things like when is it a good time to defrag, etc.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2012-Mar-07 10:18:53 by tstclair:</em> <br/>\n\nAssigned to gthain for redistribution.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2012-Mar-15 16:13:23 by tstclair:</em> <br/>\n\nReopening to add <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotMemory\" title=\"Total Slot Memory\">TotalSlotMemory</a></span> and <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotDisk\" title=\"Total Slot Disk\">TotalSlotDisk</a></span></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Mar-16 09:49</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=30940\">[30940]</a></span>: Remove warning ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2869\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2869'); return false;\" title=\"Add attribute to denote TotalSlotCpus for pSlot queries\">#2869</a></span>  (By Timothy St. Clair )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Mar-16 08:57</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=30935\">[30935]</a></span>: Added <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotMemory\" title=\"Total Slot Memory\">TotalSlotMemory</a></span> &amp;&amp; <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotDisk\" title=\"Total Slot Disk\">TotalSlotDisk</a></span> to the list pSlot attributes as there can be multiple pSlots on a machine and which helps with constraint queries. ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2869\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2869'); return false;\" title=\"Add attribute to denote TotalSlotCpus for pSlot queries\">#2869</a></span>  (By Timothy St. Clair )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Mar-07 10:17</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=30848\">[30848]</a></span>: Add attribute <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=TotalSlotCpus\" title=\"Total Slot Cpus\">TotalSlotCpus</a></span> to the list which is useful for queries. ===GT:Fixed=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2869\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2869'); return false;\" title=\"Add attribute to denote TotalSlotCpus for pSlot queries\">#2869</a></span>  (By Timothy St. Clair )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2012-May-07 16:04", "status": "resolved", "created": "2012-Mar-07 09:47", "fixed_version": "2012-Mar-0